<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - SCPIE started as buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - SCPIE started as buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers said it initiated coverage of SCPIE Holdings Inc with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- said SCPIE now writes about $125 million of gross premiums annually. Salomon said it expects this figure to grow by 10-12 percent in each of the next three years and beyond.</p>
<p>-- set a 1997 earnings estimate of $2.05 a share and a 1998 estimate of $2.25.</p>
<p>-- SCPIE was up 1/8 to 22-3/8 in morning trading.</p>
<p>((--Wall Street Desk 212-859-1730))</p>
